{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/begini-sulitnya-mencari-lokasi-untuk-setting-gundala/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Begini Sulitnya Mencari Lokasi Untuk Setting Gundala","content":"\n<p><strong>Jakarta, 4 September 2019</strong> &#8211; Pendekatan realis yang ditampilkan di film ‘Gundala’ menjadi salah satu poin penting yang paling banyak dipuji penonton. Seperti kehendak Joko Anwar, film ‘Gundala’ memang terlihat akrab di masyarakat, penggunaan lokasi yang nyata menambah kedekatan tersebut.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Blogger <a href=\"https://www.dianrestuagustina.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Dian Restu Agustina (opens in a new tab)\">Dian Restu Agustina</a> mengatakan melalui akun Twitter-nya, “Senangnya nonton Gundala akan mendapati berbagai lokasi yg dekat dengan kehidupan keseharian masyarakat Indonesia. Jadi ada rumah petakan, pasar, pabrik, perlintasan kereta, pelabuhan&#8230;dan semua itu beneran, bukan di studio yang dibuat ala-ala.”</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55526\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/begini-sulitnya-mencari-lokasi-untuk-setting-gundala/attachment/01-setting-gundala/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-setting-gundala.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-setting-gundala\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-setting-gundala-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-setting-gundala.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-setting-gundala.jpg\" alt=\"Rel kereta jadi salah satu setting Gundala yang ikonik. Sumber: Poplicist / Bumilangit\" class=\"wp-image-55526\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-setting-gundala.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-setting-gundala-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Rel kereta jadi salah satu setting Gundala yang ikonik. Sumber: Poplicist / Bumilangit</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Colorist Marvel yang telah mengerjakan banyak komik Amerika Serikat, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sunnygho/?hl=id\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Sunny Gho (opens in a new tab)\">Sunny Gho</a> ikut memberikan pujian. “Yang scout lokasi buat #Gundala siapa sih, pengen gw peluk kalo orangnya mau. Keren banget lokasi2nya. Semoga belum habis lokasi keren buat yang film2 selanjutnya,” cuitnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Demi membuat film yang keren, Joko Anwar dan tim pembuat film ‘Gundala’ bekerja keras untuk mencari lokasi. Diakui olehnya, lokasi adalah hal tersusah yang harus dihadapi dalam pembuatan film ‘Gundala’. Apalagi di Indonesia belum sering digunakan teknologi <em>green screen </em>untuk menghadirkan lokasi yang cocok demi cerita.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Baca Juga: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-gundala-jadi-harapan-baru-film-superhero-indonesia/\" target=\"_blank\">Review Film Gundala: Harapan Baru Film Superhero Indonesia</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55527\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/begini-sulitnya-mencari-lokasi-untuk-setting-gundala/attachment/02-setting-gundala/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-setting-gundala.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-setting-gundala\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-setting-gundala-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-setting-gundala.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-setting-gundala.jpg\" alt=\"Joko Anwar. Sumber: Poplicist / Bumilangit\" class=\"wp-image-55527\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-setting-gundala.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-setting-gundala-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Joko Anwar. Sumber: Poplicist / Bumilangit</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Joko\nAnwar menyampaikan bahwa semua lokasi yang digunakan di Gundala adalah lokasi\nasli. “Rumah susun, stasiun kereta, percetakan, pasar tradisional, dan\nlain-lain. Memang demikian lah situasi asli Indonesia saat ini. Jadi\nsetting-nya juga saat ini.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ia menambahkan,  “Paling seru waktu cari lokasi buat #Gundala karen harus real. Bukan saja supaya Gundala terlihat organik, tapi memang untuk syuting pake <em>full green screen</em> bujetnya gak nyampe (1/1000 Marvel DC) padahal enak tuh full AC, tapi harus bisa kita bikin walau ekstra energi.”</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55528\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/begini-sulitnya-mencari-lokasi-untuk-setting-gundala/attachment/03-setting-gundala/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-setting-gundala.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-setting-gundala\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-setting-gundala-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-setting-gundala.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-setting-gundala.jpg\" alt=\"Shooting adegan intro. Sumber: Poplicist / Bumilangit\" class=\"wp-image-55528\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-setting-gundala.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-setting-gundala-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Shooting adegan intro. Sumber: Poplicist / Bumilangit</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>“Buat\nngedapetin gambar yg bagus, sering banget kita pindah-pindah supaya penonton\nliat hasil terbaik. Misalnya adegan pasar: dalam pasar di Bogor, depan pasar di\nTangerang, samping pasar di Jakarta Kota. Gapapa capek asal yg terbaik buat\npenonton,” cuitnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Satu lagi trivia darinya adalah, “Oiya. Lokasi rumah susun Sancaka kebetulan adalah rumah tempat saya tinggal beberapa waktu lalu. Dekat kamar rusun saya juga.”</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55529\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/begini-sulitnya-mencari-lokasi-untuk-setting-gundala/attachment/04-setting-gundala/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-setting-gundala.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-setting-gundala\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-setting-gundala-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-setting-gundala.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-setting-gundala.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Poplicist / Bumilangit\" class=\"wp-image-55529\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-setting-gundala.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-setting-gundala-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Poplicist / Bumilangit</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tonton\nGundala yang sedang tayang di bioskop seluruh Indonesia untuk melihat bagaimana\nkerennya Indonesia melalui sudut pandang yang berbeda. Sampai hari kelima\n‘Gundala’ sudah ditonton lebih dari 800 ribu penonton. Bumilangit Studios,\nScreenplay Films bekerja sama dengan Legacy Pictures dan Ideosource\nentertainment mempersembahkan film ‘Gundala’ yang mulai tayang dari 29 Agustus\n2019.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"eae47db0-ae48-5fac-994f-97025a4e5d2e"}}}